</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="265" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph blockId="4.[125,1330,3092,3480]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[125,383,3332,3361]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but based on data from other species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Raffles" authorityYear="1821" box="[558,648,3371,3400]" class="Mammalia" family="Tupaiidae" genus="Tupaia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scandentia" pageId="4" pageNumber="265" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Tupaia</taxonomicName>
, food items of the Sumatran Treeshrew are presumably invertebrates and fruit.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[126,498,3451,3480]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="4.[125,1330,3092,3480]" box="[126,498,3451,3480]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[126,260,3451,3480]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">Breeding.</emphasis>
