</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="265" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="4.[1386,2597,289,683]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1387,1625,289,322]" pageId="4" pageNumber="265">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but the Sumatran Treeshrew is presumably diurnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
